---
title: Caramelized Onion Veggie Burgers with Beyond Meat®, Garlic Aioli and Baked Cauliflower 'Frites'
description: One of our favourites: the Caramelized Onion Veggie Burger – caramelized onions, spinach, soft brioche buns and Beyond Meat® patties. Roasted cauliflower 'frites' and garlic aioli make the perfect sides.
